description: SwItem: Table recording software item details for Ericsson RAN equipment in different cells and areas, including timestamps, identifiers, and metadata.  dateTime: Timestamp of record; Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site; Id2: Duplicate of CellId; Id3: Unknown identifier (likely redundant); Id4: Software item identifier; vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format; SwItem.administrativeData: Administrative data (empty); SwItem.userLabel: User-defined label (empty); SwItem.swItemId: Software item ID; SwItem.additionalInfo: Additional information (empty); SwItem.consistsOf: List of constituent components (empty).
